hopobject.name: Page
hopobject.body: I'm a trainee heritage village pharmacy southbury ct I was thrilled to see that Downsize employs registered dietitians at their locations – I'm an RD myself, after all. Jennifer Vimbor, the nutritionist at the Chicago location, told me, "We encourage a 'no diet' approach, focusing on realistic, individual goals and provide nutrition and lifestyle classes and cooking demos. The gym is a community where we all work together – clients, nutritionists and trainers."
